{"tid":996404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"神級混血正妹　電眼美乳狂吸21.5萬粉絲","createTime":"2019-01-26T09:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T14:31:28.000Z","uid":147522,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"65e49649ad36431a78e8b06b19588785d74186d4","tid":996404,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:15:09.000Z","msg":"IG坐擁21.5萬粉絲的神級混血正妹來啦！ 今年8月才滿26歲的模特兒羅莎琳（Rossarin Klinhom），是泰國、紐西蘭混血兒，皮膚白皙身材又辣，一雙迷濛大眼電擊了許多台、港、中男性粉絲，在網路論壇非常受歡迎。台灣粉絲覺得羅莎琳神似台灣「宅男女神」拐拐；中國粉絲則是拿她和楊冪比較。不管她像誰，絕對是美女無誤！<br />\n<br />\n於曼谷出生、奧克蘭長大的羅莎琳，五官有著東方美，輪廓深邃卻又是西方特色，是東西合璧的可人兒，最讓粉絲傾倒的莫過於她的甜美笑容，看起來有夠清純。她平時也喜歡分享自己的泳裝照，如果視線稍微往下挪一點，完美胸型火辣性感，完全藏不住啊！<br />\n<br />\n羅莎琳不但是貨真價實的IG網美，她還創立了自己的服裝品牌，利用外貌優勢推銷自家衣服，是不是很有生意頭腦呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mo6PiGj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMo6PiGj.png&h=a26387c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PjoNPN0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPjoNPN0.png&h=cff50713&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MN9Jn71.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMN9Jn71.png&h=e87521b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3cb1061d0e7f66e47319b7a62044b59a5d3f1e4","tid":996404,"uid":217562,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"下唇肥美夠淫賤"},{"pid":"e7808f899d32581ac99ac1ef27381804c06848a1","tid":996404,"uid":34241,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:30:19.000Z","msg":"手勢幾好"},{"pid":"c1a69682208d4f2389132fedfa0159272b669838","tid":996404,"uid":133450,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:36:22.000Z","msg":"有鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d991810f88dba8c5439a04b6feb12d970c055c","tid":996404,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"第一張影得幾靚"},{"pid":"511d340dba715ade590a354f1da68